---
import Section from '../elements/Section.astro';
import SectionIntro from '../elements/SectionIntro.astro';
import SectionTitle from '../elements/SectionTitle.astro';
import ValueCard from '../elements/ValueCard.astro';
---

<Section cssClass="section--value" title="value">
  <SectionIntro>
    <SectionTitle title="My values" />
    <p class="animate-fade">
      The principles that guide how I work — from first commit to final launch.
    </p>
  </SectionIntro>
  <div class="value-grid">
    <ValueCard icon="rocket" title="Rapid Development">
      <p>
        Tight deadlines are the norm in enterprise work. I write fast, but I don't cut corners — the
        output is clean, tested, and ready to ship.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>

    <ValueCard icon="cogs" title="Enterprise Experience">
      <p>
        I've built for the big names — Fortune 500 brands, global banks, pharma companies — using
        Sitecore, Optimizely, and custom React apps.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>

    <ValueCard icon="users" title="Team Collaboration">
      <p>
        I speak designer and I speak developer. I ask good questions, document my work, and don't
        leave teammates guessing.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>

    <ValueCard icon="lightbulb" title="Tech Stack Versatility">
      <p>
        I've shipped in React, Angular, Vue, Svelte, and whatever else the project called for. New
        tools don't slow me down.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>

    <ValueCard icon="chart-line" title="Business Impact">
      <p>
        Better Lighthouse scores, smoother UX, faster launches — I keep the bigger picture in mind
        when writing code.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>

    <ValueCard icon="star" title="Reliability">
      <p>
        I show up, I follow through, and I take pride in the work. If I say it'll be done, it'll be
        done.
      </p>
    </ValueCard>
  </div>
</Section>
